---
---
<section id="how-it-works" class="py-16 md:py-32 px-4 md:px-8">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-12 md:mb-16 text-center tracking-tight">
      Tres pasos para una
      <span class="text-gradient">economía circular</span> inteligente.
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-2xl group hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-primary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">account_balance</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold mb-4">
          Recarga tu monedero sin complicaciones.
        </h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
          Vincula tu tarjeta y recarga saldo que se convierte en activo
          digital transparente dentro del campus.
        </p>
      </div>
      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-2xl group hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-secondary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-secondary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">qr_code_scanner</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold mb-4">
          Paga al instante escaneando un QR.
        </h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
          Escanea en cafetería o kiosko. Tu pago se procesa en
          milisegundos sin comisiones intermedias.
        </p>
      </div>
      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-2xl group hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-tertiary/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-tertiary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">redeem</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold mb-4">
          Obtén recompensas por el ahorro.
        </h3>
        <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
          El ahorro del comercio se reinvierte directamente en ti con
          vales digitales automáticos y beneficios.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>